import React from 'react'
import { Logo, Nav, NavButton } from '../styles/nav'
import { Page } from '../styles/Page'

const Profile = () => {
    return (
        <Page>
            
            <Nav>
                <Logo>
                    Zumthor
                </Logo>
                
                <NavButton>
                    Sair
                </NavButton>                               
            </Nav>

        </Page>
    )
}

export default Profile
